(139, 'Sonik 2 Burner Table Top Gas Cooker With Auto-ignition - SGS-207', 'Home and Office', '', 18, 19, 28000, 10, 'Sonik Table Top Gas Cooker with 2 burner gas, beautifully crafted with maximum safety standards, style, and high performance under the best specifications. It is low in gas consumption, has automatic electronic ignition, a detachable trivet and tray for easy cleaning, and is space-saving. Itâs an efficient gas cooker that helps you save time because it gets your cooking done quickly. Itâs a more convenient, functional, and elegant addition to your kitchen.', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772723562\\/imagnified\\/bfvljzz6kyw9irxgogzx.jpg\"]', 3, 0, '2025-06-26 01:30:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 31111.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
