(144, 'Boscon 2 Litres Electric Kettle (BOS-EK20S) 2.0L', 'Home and Office', '', 18, 19, 8527, 5, 'This Electric Kettle is stylish yet simple.\r\nPerfect for every kitchen with its stainless steel body, you can be sure to have access to boiled water every time. The Electric Jug S-403SS Stainless steel body comes with a detachable cord that connects to the power source. It also features an automatic turn-off once it reaches boiling point and it rapidly boils up to 1.8Litre.', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772723568\\/imagnified\\/tmmvqzhfy6qzxz9hkd8q.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772723569\\/imagnified\\/om6bkd8z05hogfnn5hvk.jpg\"]', 3, 0, '2025-06-26 01:30:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 9474.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
