(427, 'Nexus 16\" Rechargeable Fan with USB + Remote - NX-RF4521Ri', 'Home and Office', '', 18, 19, 91799, 0, 'The Nexus 16\" Rechargeable Fan with USB + Remote - S-4531R will provide you with refreshing air all through the day; it is very reliable and efficient. This fan is an essential appliance for every home. It consists of 16-inch rotating blades, to offer you cool air when fully charged. It has dual functionality; this rechargeable standing fan on Jumia operates with electricity while charging itself at the same time. So whenever there is power cut, it will not stop working, it switches to battery mode and continues working for several hours. This fan can be used both indoors and outdoors. It is made with quality materials to ensure that it lasts very long and that you get value for your money.', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725040\\/imagnified\\/zpyczwx16alwuj40abnd.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725041\\/imagnified\\/kpdgube7v9u76vuweh1e.jpg\"]', 100, 0, '2025-06-26 01:30:27', 1, 73439.20, '2026-03-06 15:32:06', '2026-03-13 15:32:06', 101999.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
