(502, 'Newly Improved Rugged Stationary Bike With LCD Display', 'Computing', '', 1, NULL, 225000, 0, 'Indoor cycling is an ideal exercise to improve your cardiovascular system. Your heart and lungs make up your cardiovascular system, and the fitter you become, the more efficiently they work. Consistent cycling improves blood flow throughout your body and increases the speed by which oxygen is distributed. Over time, it will help improve heart and lung performance and increase your overall fitness level. This spinning bike has an LCD Monitor which displays  Time, Speed, Distance, Calorie and Pulse. It is made with strong materials for maximum durability. The bike comes in the most recent design and feature. Consistent use will help you meet your fitness goal. It is a must have for everyone as it is durable and affordable. You will love this bike.', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725161\\/imagnified\\/qwah5yzgtjasgckvkdst.jpg\"]', 100, 0, '2025-06-26 01:30:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 250000.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
