(507, 'Half-Finger Gloves Tactical Non-slip Adjustable', 'Fashion', '', 5, 21, 9473, 5, '?Slip Resistance and Abrasion Resistance?: The surface of the gloves uses special materials to effectively increase friction and prevent hands from slipping, suitable for various occasions where grip is required.\r\n?Breathability and Comfort?: The inside of the gloves uses breathable materials to effectively sweat and keep the hands dry, improving wearing comfort.\r\n?Tactical Design?: The appearance of the gloves has a tactical style, suitable for matching various mili-tary and police equipment, improving personal safety performance.\r\n?Universal Use for All Seasons?: The gloves are suitable for all seasons of the year, with good warmth and breathability.\r\n?Adjustable Wrist Design?: The gloves have an adjustable wrist design, which can be adjusted according to the thickness of the individual wrists, providing a better wearing experience.', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725173\\/imagnified\\/ltdrispg8xwegitmwce6.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725174\\/imagnified\\/huktnryl2ymykkyywus3.jpg\"]', 100, 0, '2025-06-26 01:30:27', 1, 7578.40, '2026-03-06 15:32:06', '2026-03-13 15:32:06', 10526.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
