(518, 'Wireless Earphones Bluetooth 5.3 Slide Cover Long Life', 'Computing', '', 1, 7, 11137, 20, 'Built with BT5.3 version, it offers high data transfer speed, stable connection and low consumption.\r\n\r\nSliding cover design: latest fashion design with sliding cover ,with Track design for cover.\r\n\r\nLong working time: 4-5 hours after full single charging, charging box to charge earphone for 15-20 times.\r\n\r\nMulti-functional Tou-ch control let you take calls, switch songs, or control volume simply by touching these in-ear wireless headphones all without taking your smart phones out of your pocket.', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725193\\/imagnified\\/dhvaa8ym9fuqgngbtokx.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725194\\/imagnified\\/ray3s59pxj2supounwdl.jpg\"]', 100, 0, '2025-06-26 01:30:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 12374.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
