(607, '  Polystar 5 Litres Air Fryer (PV-K5AFM) - Black', 'Home and Office', '', 18, 19, 65000, 10, 'Its fully adjustable temperature control allows you to pre-set the best cooking temperature for your food up to 200 degrees and an integrated timer allows you to pre-set cooking times of up to 30 minutes.\r\n\r\nIts unique combination of fast circulating hot air and a grill element allows you to fry a variety of delicious fried meals in a fast and easy way.\r\n\r\nThe Air Fryer makes use of air for frying so the smell and vapour of traditional frying is unavailable. Enjoy easy, safe and economical cleaning everyday without retaining the fry smell.', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725369\\/imagnified\\/vjwf0qqlx42fpiue7pn4.jpg\"]', 100, 0, '2025-06-26 01:30:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 72222.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
