(625, 'Crown Star 3.5L Stainless Electric Deep Fryer', 'Home and Office', '', 18, 19, 67000, 10, 'This deep fryer from Master Chef with a capacity of 3.5 litres, provides plenty of room for whatever you might want to fry! The adjustable temperature control will allow you get the precise frying temperature you need. Plus, youâll be able to peek at your food and check its progress thanks to a glass window on top of the lid. And itâs also easy to clean up after frying is done due to its fixed non-stick pot.DurableEasy to operate and useTemperature controlRemovable parts3.5 Liters', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725389\\/imagnified\\/xo14grxcnxpnf1lvcs55.jpg\"]', 100, 0, '2025-06-26 01:30:27', 1, 53600.00, '2026-03-06 15:32:06', '2026-03-13 15:32:06', 74444.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
