(657, '7KG 1000W Electric Clothes Dryer Wardrobe Energy Save', '', '', 18, 19, 90000, 5, 'Portable electronic tumble dryer is extremely suitable for damp, cold or rainy weather and helps you dry and disinfect your different clothes as well as a variety of textiles. For drying, the laundry can be hung on the hanger so that your clothes do not get creased, so this corresponds to a steam iron.\r\nThis is a dryer that does not require assembly. It only takes 30 seconds to start working, and the folding is completed within 15 seconds. It does not need to be completely disassembled. Unlike other dryers, it requires no complicated installation steps and can be used at any time. And it is more convenient when folded and resembles the 20-inch boarding case.', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725888\\/imagnified\\/joojc3xpoj9zezx2wijh.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772725889\\/imagnified\\/rzliczxdty2rkboc0xbv.jpg\"]', 100, 0, '2025-06-26 01:30:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 100000.00, NULL, '', NULL, 0, 0),
