(998, 'Pixma TS704 Wireless Photo, CD, ID Card And A4 Paper Printer With ID Card Tray', 'Computing', '', 1, 7, 209369, 5, 'DescriptionBig in features but small in size,  smallest-ever 5-ink single function printer has a large 350-sheet capacity to deliver professional documents and high-quality photos with seamless connectivity - and all for an affordable price.Connect to Ethernet or link a laptop, PC or smart device at the touch of a button and print with the PRINT app, AirPrint (iOS), Mopria (Android) or Windows 10 Mobile.Benefit from uninterrupted printing with a high plain paper capacity of 350 sheets and 2-way paper feed. Monitor ink levels via the LCD, which will show you its status at a glance.Save paper with auto 2-sided printing and up efficiency with high-yield cartridges', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772726536\\/imagnified\\/k0gc83gpejjojdvbzabv.jpg\"]', 200, 0, '2025-06-26 01:30:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 232632.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
