(1880, 'Scarlett 7 Speed Electric Hand Mixer Whisk Egg Beater Cake Baking', 'Home and Office', '', 18, 19, 10000, 10, 'â¢ Whisk: Electric acceleration make the mixer suitable for various stirring. Whisk eggs with one hand in 30 seconds to easily make desserts.\r\n\r\nâ¢ 7 Speeds: 7 gears speed control allows you to mix a variety of ingredients to make delicious desserts. At speed 1-2 to stir batter, speed 3 to whip , speed 4 to make watermelon juice, speed 5 to mix milkshakes, and speeds 6-7 to whisk eggs.\r\n\r\nâ¢ Easy to Change Whisk: This pack contains 2 beater hooks and 2 mixer hooks. You can easily and quickly remove the whisk from the hand mixer moving the gear key to the 0 positions and press the key.\r\n\r\nâ¢ Ergonomic Grip Design: The ergonomic handle gives a comfortable grip, for excellent balance and control. It is effortless to mix heavy ingredients.\r\n\r\nâ¢ Make a Variety of Food: It is ideal for mixing heavy ingredients to make soft bread, fragrant spongecake, silky chocolate, watermelon juice, milkshakes, tarts, souffle, etc.\r\n\r\nâ¢After-sales Service Guarantee: Any problem, please contact our store withou', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772734130\\/imagnified\\/c4lyq1duhyykg7fj2qgg.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772734131\\/imagnified\\/ohstwrbzasa0c4i2lgzm.jpg\"]', 50, 0, '2025-06-26 15:03:43', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 11111.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
