(1945, 'OPPO A5s 99.9% NEW 4GB RAM + 64GB Expanded Storage 4230mAh 6.2\" HD+ Display Dual Camera AI Selfie Face Unlock Smartphone', 'Phones & Tablets', '', 4, 10, 109286, 30, 'The OPPO A5s is an affordable and feature-packed smartphone designed to cater to a wide range of user needs. Here are five key highlights of this device:\r\n\r\n1. **Reliable Performance**: Powered by a MediaTek Helio P35 processor and6GB of RAM, the OPPO A5s offers smooth and efficient performance. Whether multitasking between apps, streaming videos, or casual gaming, this phone ensures a seamless user experience.\r\n\r\n2. **Ample Storage**: With 128GB of internal storage, the A5s provides plenty of space for your apps, photos, videos, and other files. The storage is expandable via a microSD card up to 256GB, giving you the flexibility to store even more of your digital content.\r\n\r\n3. **Vibrant Display**: The phone features a 6.2-inch HD+ display with a waterdrop notch, delivering vibrant colors and sharp visuals. This large screen is perfect for enjoying multimedia content, browsing the internet, and engaging on social media.\r\n\r\n4. **Dual Camera System**: The OPPO A5s is equipped with a 13MP main camera , allowing you to capture beautiful photos with excellent depth and clarity. The 8MP front camera is ideal for selfies and video calls, ensuring clear and detailed images.\r\n\r\n5. **Long-lasting Battery**: A 4230mAh battery powers the A5s, providing extended usage time on a single charge. This long-lasting battery life is essential for users who need their phone to last throughout the day without frequent recharging.\r\n\r\nFor the African market, a standout feature of the OPPO A5s is its durability and reliability. The robust build quality and efficient battery life make it suitable for various environments and conditions prevalent in the region. This ensures that users can rely on their device for both work and leisure without interruption.\r\n\r\nIn summary, the OPPO A5s combines reliable performance, ample storage, a vibrant display, a versatile camera system, and long-lasting battery life. Its durability and reliability make it particularly well-suited for the dynamic and diverse needs of the African market, ensuring users can depend on it in any situation.', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772734233\\/imagnified\\/onyfjzumbm8v9u8ihmnl.jpg\"]', 40, 0, '2025-07-06 23:11:09', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 121429.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
(1946, 'Oppo A3S 99.9%NEW 4GB RAM 64GB ROM 4230mAh 6.2-inch 13MP+2MP Front 8MP Face Unlock Smartphone?Local Customer Service?', 'Phones & Tablets', '', 4, 10, 109286, 30, '- 6.2-inch IPS LCD display with 720 x 1520 pixel resolution\r\n- Qualcomm Snapdragon 450 octa-core processor\r\n- RAM options: 2GB, 3GB, or 4GB\r\n- Storage options: 16GB, 32GB, or 64GB, expandable via microSDXC\r\n- Dual rear cameras (13MP main sensor + 2MP depth sensor)\r\n- 8MP front camera\r\n- 4230mAh non-removable battery\r\n- Android 8.1 Oreo with ColorOS 5.1\r\n- Dual SIM support\r\n- Rear-mounted fingerprint sensor', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772734234\\/imagnified\\/vco7am5yzv9vjh5lr3ui.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772734234\\/imagnified\\/ajonoapxyysfoi0v11ba.jpg\"]', 30, 0, '2025-07-06 23:15:08', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 121429.00, NULL, 'none', NULL, 0, 0),
(1947, 'OPPO A5s 99.9% NEW 4GB RAM + 64GB Expanded Storage 4230mAh 6.2\" HD+ Display Dual Camera AI Selfie Face Unlock Smartphone', 'Phones & Tablets', '', 4, 10, 109286, 30, 'The OPPO A5s is an affordable and feature-packed smartphone designed to cater to a wide range of user needs. Here are five key highlights of this device:\r\n\r\n1. **Reliable Performance**: Powered by a MediaTek Helio P35 processor and6GB of RAM, the OPPO A5s offers smooth and efficient performance. Whether multitasking between apps, streaming videos, or casual gaming, this phone ensures a seamless user experience.\r\n\r\n2. **Ample Storage**: With 128GB of internal storage, the A5s provides plenty of space for your apps, photos, videos, and other files. The storage is expandable via a microSD card up to 256GB, giving you the flexibility to store even more of your digital content.\r\n\r\n3. **Vibrant Display**: The phone features a 6.2-inch HD+ display with a waterdrop notch, delivering vibrant colors and sharp visuals. This large screen is perfect for enjoying multimedia content, browsing the internet, and engaging on social media.\r\n\r\n4. **Dual Camera System**: The OPPO A5s is equipped with a 13MP main camera , allowing you to capture beautiful photos with excellent depth and clarity. The 8MP front camera is ideal for selfies and video calls, ensuring clear and detailed images.\r\n\r\n5. **Long-lasting Battery**: A 4230mAh battery powers the A5s, providing extended usage time on a single charge. This long-lasting battery life is essential for users who need their phone to last throughout the day without frequent recharging.\r\n', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772734235\\/imagnified\\/noqyjm0fdd6tqssaxag1.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772734236\\/imagnified\\/qxnsibkvqvjtqbtfnyiv.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772734238\\/imagnified\\/pvm33ru2gm