(2051, 'Luxury Set Of 4 Travelling Trolley Box', 'Fashion', '', 5, 21, 243750, 20, 'Polyester fabric is used to construct luggage set, making it lightweight, durable, flexible. Its light weight makes traveling a joy as well. The lightweight but strong structure ensures long-term use and safety.\r\n2 Swivel wheels that can be rotated with easily movement to your convenience.\r\nYour belongings can be easily separated into two compartments, one with a cross strap and the other with a zipper for your convenience.\r\n\r\nIts top handle help in controlling movement, and its side handles facilitate removal from locations where wheels are impractical.\r\n\r\nLuggage 4 Pieces set available Dimensions and Weight - 20 Inch (53 H x 36 W x 25 D cm)  24 Inch (63 H x 41 W x 28 D cm) \r\n\r\n28 Inch (73 H x 46 W x 31 D cm) \r\n\r\nYou can lock your belongings away with a three-digit combination without having to worry about managing a key. You can save the combination digit on your phone or notebook if you frequently forget things', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1772734716\\/imagnified\\/aeono6vgl97pq9467zfg.jpg\"]', 15, 0, '2025-11-23 11:59:56', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
(2052, 'LOVE Design Travel Box With Kit Bag - 4sets', 'Fashion', '', 5, 21, 175000, 20, 'This 3 set Trolley Luggage Box with a kit bag is a a must-have. It comes in different sizes to accommodate all your travel needs. It has neat interior lining and an inner belt to properly hold all your contents. No matter how much you toss the suitcase around when travelling, your clothes will be well secured. Each suitcase has 4 wheels and a trolley handle which makes it easy for you to move around an airport or train station. Its 3-digit combination lock ensures that all your contents are safe at all times. One Piece Travel Suitcases has a lovely color which makes it more suited to men and women. It is made from the finest plastic material which ensures high durability . This suitcase will wear well, last longer and look better even after extensive use. One nice thing about this travel box is that it is lightweight so you can easily carry around without experiencing any form of discomfort. Pack up with ease and travel to wherever with these well-designed luggage box. What stands this suitcase out from the rest is that it offers security, waterproof ,durability and convenient mobility.    This 3 set Trolley Luggage Box with a kit bag is a a must-have. It comes in different sizes to accommodate all your travel needs. It has neat interior lining and an inner belt to properly hold all your contents. No matter how much you toss the suitcase around when travelling, your clothes will be well secured. Each suitcase has 4 wheels and a trolley handle which makes it easy for you to move around an airport or train station. Its 3-digit combination lock ensures that all your contents are safe at all times. One Piece Travel Suitcases has a lovely color which makes it more suited to men and women. It is made from the finest plastic material which ensures high durability . This suitcase will wear well, last longer and look better even after extensive use. One nice thing about this travel box i