(4119, '1:4 Scale Remote Control Cars for Kids, Sport Car Models, Building Kits', 'Home and Office', 'Home Appliances', 18, 19, 24700, 5, 'Challenge your building skills with 1314 pieces: This complex building set offers a rewarding challenge for children and adults alike, encouraging concentration, problem-solving, and fine motor skills.\r\nDetailed Supercar Model: Recreate a sleek and powerful supercar with precision, capturing its iconic design and intricate details.\r\nDurable, High-Quality Bricks: Made of durable, high-quality ABS plastic, these bricks are designed for long-lasting fun and withstand repeated play. Creative Play and Display: Once built, this supercar model makes a captivating display piece, showcasing your building prowess and adding a touch of style to any room.\r\nEducational and Engaging: This building set stimulates imagination, creativity, and spatial reasoning, making it a fun and educational experience for all ages.', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1773354592\\/products\\/pzl5njgfkikvfsb9fa64.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1773354593\\/products\\/xleny9fm4khpyjcfi4rh.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1773354595\\/products\\/caxvij8xmkxem8u59hns.jpg\",\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1773354596\\/products\\/nlsgttgxztrdfdygwmp5.jpg\"]', 7, 0, '2026-03-12 22:29:56', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, 0, 1),
