(4193, 'Hennessy XO Cognac - 750ml', 'Groceries', '', 16, 0, 410000, 5, 'The Hennessy X.O. cognac was created by Maurice Hennessy in 1870 for his circle of friends and introduced a new style of cognac.\r\nHennessy X.O is the emblematic icon of the House. Its cognac taste makes you enjoy a unique sensorial experience, while its intense and deep colour is a sign of its robustness. Flavours of candied fruit and subtle lightly spiced tones develop on the palate in complete harmony. The infinite echo expresses all the complexity of the cognac\'s blending and its long ageing process.\r\nHennessy X.O remains the reference.\r\n\r\nTASTING NOTES:\r\nA DEEP AND COMPLEX âEXTRA OLDâ\r\n\r\nAPPEARANCE\r\nA deep and intense amber with glimpses of mahogany, X.O is notably darker than the rest of our collection.\r\n\r\nAROMA\r\nScents of candied fruit combine with a subtle, lightly spicy nose, giving X.O its unmistakable aroma.\r\n\r\nTASTE\r\nX.O has a powerful, albeit soft, tonality, with hints of cocoa and a warm, fruity presence, followed by a tremendous length.\r\n\r\nThis item is Non- Refundable', 0, 'Trollz Store', 'Yes', '[\"https:\\/\\/res.cloudinary.com\\/dg4vrra76\\/image\\/upload\\/v1773422799\\/products\\/phmn3lhzazdcjfq0blr5.jpg\"]', 5, 0, '2026-03-13 17:26:39', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, 0, 0),
